  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Telbivudine on Liver Cirrhosis in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis B (CHB)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Clinical Study of Telbivudine on Liver Cirrhosis in Patients With Chronic Hepatitis B</official_title>
